{"tid":251554,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"日本強勁止痛藥","createTime":"2017-05-21T04:55:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-21T15:27:44.000Z","uid":36798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"32765f3be2cde642f9b04818d480aac9abc7d3d6","tid":251554,"uid":36798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T04:55:21.000Z","msg":"我去日本嗰陣買左隻止痛藥<br />\n雖然寫食兩粒一次<br />\n但係我食一粒已經可以唔痛<br />\n上網search又搵唔到呢隻究竟咩野黎<br />\n又唔知副作用勁唔勁<br />\n有冇人食過呢隻野<br />\n或者睇得明日文<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/21/125508_53cf7d354ec8e8f8cfdda4913196442f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F21%2F125508_53cf7d354ec8e8f8cfdda4913196442f.jpg&h=5f143138&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/21/125510_17c6911a866d58def5dd58bf852eeed0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F21%2F125510_17c6911a866d58def5dd58bf852eeed0.jpg&h=ace56f57&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cec440182e5f82c57f52b78ba926258893de4a61","tid":251554,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T04:57:49.000Z","msg":"用google搵到<br />\n好似係呢隻<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.drugs.com/dosage/ibuprofen.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.drugs.com%2Fdosage%2Fibuprofen.html&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=743b8f45\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.drugs.com/dosage/ibuprofen.html</a>"},{"pid":"0921c2448f36a30f13dbe1b8b1fe614923c2454e","tid":251554,"uid":36798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T05:06:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用google搵到<br />\n好似係呢隻<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.drugs.com/dosage/ibuprofen.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.drugs.com%2