g":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用google搵到<br />\n好似係呢隻<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.drugs.com/dosage/ibuprofen.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.drugs.com%2Fdosage%2Fibuprofen.html&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=743b8f45\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.drugs.com/dosage/ibuprofen.html</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你識日文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ngoogle 係隻藥個成分?<br />\nThanks!!!</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nIbuprofen 一街都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似勁過香港d止痛藥<br />\n我勁我唔知食左乜落肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個成份香港好似要醫生處方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一般貨識嚟 唔關咩日本事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你係非洲買 都可以叫非洲強勁止痛藥"},{"pid":"ace494e140c2820858ac2d5820195c3ccfa7e4c6","tid":251554,"uid":28884,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T05:43:22.000Z","msg":"小心胃有事"},{"pid":"6e428e0c75573a9753b759790a134b573d4fc530","tid":251554,"uid":52943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T05:47:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食佢不如食Celebrex，唔傷胃</blockquote><br />\n痛博士止痛效能極高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過唔係唔傷胃,有啲人戇鳩鳩走去買400mg唔食胃藥食到胃出血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n高劑量Celebrex配埋Omeprazole會好好多"},{"pid":"4f700c0424fb247b158ff2dd249656aadcd9cd73","tid":251554,"uid":36798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T05:50:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小心胃有事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上維基又冇話佢好傷胃<br />\n不過 EVE 都係呢隻成分"},{"pid":"8ced0403c00ec46677308b8a2f1601487e2ced25","tid":251554,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T05:53:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小心胃有事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上維基又冇話佢好傷胃<br />\n不過 EVE 都係呢隻成分</blockquote><br />\nibuprofen 傷胃, 我向你保證 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家轉左食痛博士 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港ibuprofen 唔洗醫生開但ibuprofen liquid capsule 就要醫生開, 所以我以前去美國就會買定(佢地當普通藥咁一街都係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"b488c2cc575b0cf411eb155fe9268fb9500a02a6","tid":251554,"uid":26385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T05:54:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小心胃有事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上維基又冇話佢好傷胃<br />\n不過 EVE 都係呢隻成分</blockquote><br />\nibuprofen 傷胃, 我向你保證 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家轉左食痛博士 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港ibuprofen 唔洗醫生開但ibuprofen liquid capsule 就要醫生開, 所以我以前去美國就會買定(佢地當普通藥咁一街都係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)</blockquote><br />\n去萬寧有藥劑師嘅藥房都有得買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nAdvil<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ecf16ad9778e43f90baae2b302afc4a9bcee023","tid":251554,"uid":36798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T05:56:28.000Z","msg":"必理痛又點睇？<br />\n之前一直食開"},{"pid":"20cfedf83cafceae87ad845ab3cef508f987482f","tid":251554,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T05:57:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小心胃有事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上維基又冇話佢好傷胃<br />\n不過 EVE 都係呢隻成分</blockquote><br />\nibuprofen 傷胃, 我向你保證 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家轉左食痛博士 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港ibuprofen 唔洗醫生開但ibuprofen liquid capsule 就要醫生開, 所以我以前去美國就會買定(佢地當普通藥咁一街都係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)</blockquote><br />\n去萬寧有藥劑師嘅藥房都有得買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nAdvil<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n喔係㗎? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我而家無食啦轉左藥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以前我叫佢做&ldquo;美國佬必理痛&rdquo; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c8942074058fbb72ca8955db6ca1ca8677ada78","tid":251554,"uid":37389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T05:57:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>必理痛又點睇？<br />\n之前一直食開</blockquote><br />\n垃圾"},{"pid":"4624da93aac5ab327a4efb10129a10b64ebdc888","tid":251554,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T05:58:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>必理痛又點睇？<br />\n之前一直食開</blockquote><br />\n絲打止m 痛?"},{"pid":"676dd469a3a94b8f68cf66b0048ffa010c2d3ab7","tid":251554,"uid":36798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T05:59:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>必理痛又點睇？<br />\n之前一直食開</blockquote><br />\n絲打止m 痛?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nm痛 頭痛"},{"pid":"02a3be65175cc5328bfcb7fd34e0181a76ede839","tid":251554,"uid":52051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T06:01:19.000Z","msg":"留名學野 <br />\n<br />\n我之前係日本買隻EVE, 試過佢止痛勁，但呢隻都會傷胃？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96a732de89503dcf833d93898c44ada4e6304189","tid":251554,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T06:02:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>必理痛又點睇？<br />\n之前一直食開</blockquote><br />\n絲打止m 痛?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nm痛 頭痛</blockquote><br />\n頭痛就是但食啦, m痛食痛博士, 我啲朋友話好有效(佢地係會痛到暈嗰啲)  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"217e7569aba3bf0a9307546b96cf5cb1117e5ed5","tid":251554,"uid":18953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T06:05:34.000Z","msg":"我都覺得好勁 但食完個鼻會keep 住聞到隻藥既味 <br />\n食過一排 之後唔敢食 不過真係好止痛"},{"pid":"08233fbb958a507095daf8d8890a3727012e0972","tid":251554,"uid":36798,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T06:05:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>必理痛又點睇？<br />\n之前一直食開</blockquote><br />\n絲打止m 痛?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nm痛 頭痛</blockquote><br />\n頭痛就是但食啦, m痛食痛博士, 我啲朋友話好有效(佢地係會痛到暈嗰啲)  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e441aabbacf778960a47e725b6f578b44f8d2ece","tid":251554,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T06:05:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"834e939e6cfd3c7cf25ec69ba473387c06a38a95","tid":251554,"uid":4880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T06:06:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食佢不如食Celebrex，唔傷胃</blockquote><br />\n傷心"},{"pid":"359641eab8bcf393cee8b09f1f2495e5746f5d29","tid":251554,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T06:07:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名學野 <br />\n<br />\n我之前係日本買隻EVE, 試過佢止痛勁，但呢隻都會傷胃？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nEVE 係牌子名, 你睇成份其實都係ibuprofen, 佢聲稱唔傷胃係加左&ldquo;氧化鎂&rdquo; 即係antacid, 胃藥黎, 你去藥房買pack 200mg ibuprofen 加粒胃dick素咪咁上下效果 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢有用但唔神奇亦唔係咩日本神奇止痛藥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 唔識藥劑, 只係食得藥多所以知少少 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3974264c0b555451ae0fbe241ef2e3ad5145efe2","tid":251554,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T06:07:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"31b6ba541b8ecbe26745b3d6c76cdd2c5920b8b2","tid":251554,"uid":21197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T06:08:45.000Z","msg":"偏頭痛有無話食邊隻好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e46567bc5aa8669862cb66a918820ca22aa281b","tid":251554,"uid":29461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T06:11:09.000Z","msg":"想要消炎效果，係咪Celebrex 比較安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04872f3b0c68b8e9e5566ba046dc14863786b38e","tid":251554,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T06:12:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ac07d4c2f71d427f309146f2f47cd5f8e17cf400","tid":251554,"uid":52051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T06:13:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>留名學野 <br />\n<br />\n我之前係日本買隻EVE, 試過佢止痛勁，但呢隻都會傷胃？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nEVE 係牌子名, 你睇成份其實都係ibuprofen, 佢聲稱唔傷胃係加左&ldquo;氧化鎂&rdquo; 即係antacid, 胃藥黎, 你去藥房買pack 200mg ibuprofen 加粒胃dick素咪咁上下效果 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢有用但唔神奇亦唔係咩日本神奇止痛藥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 唔識藥劑, 只係食得藥多所以知少少 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁都好d, 因為我通常都空肚食（唔係成日食）"},{"pid":"f5429b849b2d4724c3f9e95a8421055d8aeae43c","tid":251554,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T06:14:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>頭痛 m痛 食aspirin <br />\n<br />\n肌肉痛關節痛食Diclofenac<br />\n<br />\n食左兩粒藥都止唔到痛<br />\n請睇醫生</blockquote><br />\n我認同你講野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但朋友有次m 痛食左2粒藥(成藥)都痛去搵醫生,醫生開返同一隻藥比佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb0d1a52d19707bb113dade6946474a116c36518","tid":251554,"uid":29203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r