ass=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a824325c4fe1da16bb1354378f2d501e3992b0d","tid":251554,"uid":28245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T06:31:35.000Z","msg":"其實必利痛有效又安全<br />\n<br />\n覺得唔夠就打孖上 <br />\n<br />\n一日唔多過4000mg就ok"},{"pid":"c3980b6ce679a8c978d68a78b13fbf1bae25d2d2","tid":251554,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T06:31:55.000Z","msg":"日本藥唔好亂食 太勁"},{"pid":"b80af8428270a3825b0785442696bb985465244e","tid":251554,"uid":97277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T06:32:03.000Z","msg":"樓主心理作用啫<br />\nIbuprofen周街都有啦<br />\n仲要得150mg成分<br />\n我呢一盒200mg都唔需要醫生簽紙啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nnote: 請勿空肚食ibuprofen,另外請勿過量服用否則會造成胃出血（徵狀：胃漲，糞便呈黑）"},{"pid":"8649d6e83050b5c33e092e43bc19d808368cd00f","tid":251554,"uid":97277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T06:32:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主心理作用啫<br />\nIbuprofen周街都有啦<br />\n仲要得150mg成分<br />\n我呢一盒200mg都唔需要醫生簽紙啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nnote: 請勿空肚食ibuprofen,另外請勿過量服用否則會造成胃出血（徵狀：胃漲，糞便呈黑）</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/21/143256_d36827b6dcafad23179eec252cc541b7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F21%2F143256_d36827b6dcafad23179eec252cc541b7.jpg&h=d593364d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b014e9d5408e87fb3ab75d965c14e52ea2198ebc","tid":251554,"uid":19861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T06:33:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1088ef649b539f673e24ec47deb34e76c9547a6e","tid":251554,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T06:36:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5edd2792b5585ed2960b6419a70fcc40eb58b2